- content_for :header_title, 'Introduction'

.form-card
  %header.form-card__header
    .step-section-header
      - icon 'section-1'
      .step-section-header__subhead
        There are 4 sections you need to complete to submit a full application.

  .form-card__content
    .slab.slab--not-padded
      .card.card--narrow
        %h4.step-section-header__headline
          What are they?

        %ul.list--bulleted.list--padded
          %li
            %p
              %strong Household
            %p.text--small
              Information about yourself and each person in your household

          %li
            %p
              %strong Money &amp; Income
            %p.text--small
              Information about money you receive and valuable things you may
              own

          %li
            %p
              %strong Expenses
            %p.text--small
              We will ask about your expenses for things like housing,
              medicine, dependent care and more

          %li
            %p
              %strong Preferences
            %p.text--small
              We will ask about the best ways to reach you and to proceed with
              your application, plus any additional information that you might
              want to share with us.

    .slab.slab--not-padded
      .card.card--narrow
        %h3.h3--strong
          Next, describe your household for us.

        %p.text--help
          If you aren't sure about all the details right now â€” that's okay.
          Do your best and we will work with you to clarify later.

  = render partial: 'shared/next_step_link'
